title: Where are my rewards?!!??!

embed.description: 46520 / Platinum 5 69LP / 52W 45L Win Ratio 54% / Vayne - 28W 17L Win Ratio 62%, Tristana - 14W 4L Win Ratio 78%, Ezreal - 6W 9L Win Ratio 40%, Jhin - 2W 2L Win Ratio 50%, Kayle - 0W 4L Win Ratio 0%

body:
Greetings,
Today, i decided to release my stress and play a game of League of legends. As i logged in my account "46520" i notice that i i did not receive any rewards.
I ended PLatinum 5 this season I did not receive tha platinum in game border the icon nor the maokai skin nor champion! And i would also want to know if this was intend from riot or it was just a mistake. Thanks for you time.

replies.body:
We're still working on rolling out ranked rewards, as *Zombiemaster* mentioned. If you hang on for just a bit longer, we'll have those all out soon.

Let me know if you have any quesitons.
